♪Amidst the grieving woods♪

207
00:19:20,840 --> 00:19:23,350
♪Who is crying out there♪

208
00:19:26,580 --> 00:19:29,540
♪I still relentlessly hold on♪

209
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:34,420
♪I refuse to accept this destiny♪

210
00:19:35,370 --> 00:19:37,750
♪Desperately searching♪

211
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:40,170
♪Any signs of you♪

212
00:19:43,590 --> 00:19:47,290
♪The bleak Star Forest,
illuminating in the moonlight♪

213
00:19:47,430 --> 00:19:51,960
♪In your eyes, the world never changes♪

214
00:19:52,470 --> 00:19:57,100
♪Yearning grows and interweaves with the past♪

215
00:19:57,340 --> 00:20:04,140
♪Aside from promise,
I have much that I haven't told you♪

216
00:20:04,360 --> 00:20:08,460
♪You are the memory I refuse to let go♪

217
00:20:08,650 --> 00:20:12,680
♪And the craziness of my desperation♪

218
00:20:12,890 --> 00:20:14,090
♪Can you hear♪

219
00:20:14,520 --> 00:20:16,420
♪My calls♪

220
00:20:16,660 --> 00:20:18,550
♪Breaking through extreme dolours♪

221
00:20:18,550 --> 00:20:21,350
♪Rushing towards your embrace♪

222
00:20:21,540 --> 00:20:25,690
♪You are the only one
I dreamt to comb my hair♪

223
00:20:25,690 --> 00:20:29,910
♪And the wish I made upon a star♪

224
00:20:30,090 --> 00:20:31,450
♪One day♪

225
00:20:31,670 --> 00:20:34,120
♪You will turn up gorgeously♪

226
00:20:34,280 --> 00:20:36,250
♪And hold my hands♪

227
00:20:36,460 --> 00:20:42,470
♪To envisage our future♪

228
00:20:45,350 --> 00:20:45,980
[Next episode]

229
00:20:46,066 --> 00:20:47,665
Yellow Level One Test is not hard.

230
00:20:47,800 --> 00:20:49,499
Bai Chen Xiang used her wits

231
00:20:49,633 --> 00:20:50,865
and advantages...

232
00:20:51,133 --> 00:20:52,499
The pain of skipping levels
and absorbing soul rings

233
00:20:52,833 --> 00:20:54,065
is almost unbearable.

234
00:20:54,233 --> 00:20:56,699
Fatty has really changed a lot
after meeting Xiang.

235
00:20:56,866 --> 00:20:59,032
Xiang's well-being is in your hands.

236
00:21:00,166 --> 00:21:01,232
It's almost been a month.

237
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:02,365
Feel it carefully.

238
00:21:02,733 --> 00:21:05,099
Use your utmost willpower to endure it.

239
00:21:05,233 --> 00:21:08,832
You've found the true mystery
of the Light of the God of the Ocean so quickly?

240
00:21:09,300 --> 00:21:11,265
Much less Fatty, who's always carefree.

241
00:21:11,733 --> 00:21:12,599
He can definitely do it.

242
00:21:13,433 --> 00:21:15,599
No wonder the God of the Ocean chose you.

